title: Soft Decoration - Fabrics in Home Design (gnv64)
description:
Soft Decoration - Fabrics in Home Design 
by Bingxu Du 
LST Publishing House | English/Chinese | ISBN: 7538174893 | October 2012 | PDF | 256 pages | 135 mb <a href="
http://www.amazon.com/Soft-Decoration-Fabrics-Home-Design/dp/7538174893" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://www.amazon.com/Soft-Decoration-Fabrics-Home-Design/dp/7538174893</a>

The book presents diverse home decoration styles (American, European & Chinese)  with stunning pictures. It includes examples for living rooms, dining rooms, bedrooms, bathrooms, and entertaining rooms. It also shows effects of different materials in home decoration. In addition, four interior design projects are presented in details. This book is suitable for both professional and leisure reading.
